	title="GitNexus Benchmark: Graph-Indexed Retrieval vs Claude Code's Native Exploration | Ilzam"
	description="A structured comparison of GitNexus graph RAG against Claude Code's native heuristic-guided codebase traversal on a mid-sized Flutter project. Token costs, tool call overhead, KuzuDB internals, and the architectural case for graph-indexed retrieval."
>
